lead_paragraph: West Ham United have always done things their own way through thick and thin, so it was fitting when Frank Sinatra's timeless classic kickstarted a post-match party that brought the curtain down on 112 years at the Boleyn Ground on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: West Ham Do It Their Way in Fitting Boleyn Finale
